t is also involved in the generation of wind energy and exporting products. The company serves domestic and international markets. Magna Electro Castings Limited was formerly known as Magna Electronics Limited and changed its name to Magna Electro Castings Limited in December 1992. The company was incorporated in 1990 and is headquartered in Coimbatore, India."}}